1. *Dobiješ* sve informacije o događaju po pošti. (You get all the information about the event by mail.)

2. Spremna je da ti *dobiješ* nagradu. (She is ready to give you the reward.)

3. Kada *dobiješ* pravu odgovor, znam da ćeš biti zadovoljan. (When you get the right answer, I know you will be satisfied.)

4. *Dobiješ* li dovoljno bodova, možeš se upisati na fakultet. (If you get enough points, you can enroll in college.)

5. Molim da mi *dobiješ* ovu informaciju brzo. (Please get me this information quickly.)